Keela

I have an ice cold heart that apparently only Taylor can melt. 🖤

body: Am I the only one that noticed Tay doesnt kiss her love interest in Babe? He kisses her forehead and thats it. She has kissed her love interests in her past MVs but I feel like, because Joe is the real deal, she wont do that for as long as theyre together (which is forevermore in case you were wondering)
